                            						  	<p class="text-justify">
                            						  		VCP has spacious, ventilated, well furnished, modernized and IT enabled&nbsp;classrooms which creates healthy atmosphere for the students and are well lit and echo- proof to facilitate&nbsp;the teaching-learning process. Classrooms are designed for conventional lectures and group discussions. These facilities create an ideal atmosphere well suited for teaching-learning pedagogy. 
