                                                        <div>
                            						  		<p class="text-justify">In addition to state-of-the-art machinery, the Vaageswari College of Pharmacy labs have sufficient glassware and tools to give students practical training to help them succeed in their profession. Our Institution is having sufficient numbers of labs for providing B. Pharmacy, M. Pharmacy, Pharm. D, and Pharm. D (PB) training in all practical needs of pharmacy. All labs are equipped with enough work space as per the standard specifications of JNTUH, as well as PCI- New Delhi. Safety is the primary criteria in Pharma laboratories, all of our labs are well equipped with safety measures.</p>
                            								<p class="text-justify">College has centralized instrumentation room where all sophisticated instruments are available to students for their research as well as routine lab work.</p>
                            								<p class="text-justify">Vaageswari College of Pharmacy has MOU with Chalmeda Anand Rao Institute of Medical Sciences (CAIMS) Karimnagar, which ensures training in Clinical Pharmacy Practice for successful completion of the Pharm D and Pharm D (PB) course curriculum.</p>
