                            								<p class="text-justify">Medicinal plants have played an important role in human healthcare as the essential ingredients of traditional medicines for thousands of years. Botanical gardens worldwide play a crucial role in the conservation, cultivation and utilization of plant species, and research activities related to ecology, taxonomy, systematic, biotechnology, etc. Medicinal plant gardens have played a significant role in education and research of plant species used for medicinal purposes. Our Institution is having medicinal garden with variety of medicinal plants as per the requirements of pharmacy curriculum. Where, we are maintaining endangering plant species.</p>
